        {
            "id": 6346727,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 科斯塔集團(CSGP-US)大漲5.08%，報48.07美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科斯塔集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CSGP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CSGP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CSGP-US</a>)截至台北時間19日00:10股價上漲2.33美元，報48.07美元，漲幅5.08%，成交量1,357,535（股），盤中最高價48.07美元、最低價46.37美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.61%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.87%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.3%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.81%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>科斯塔集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CSGP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CSGP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CSGP-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-11.52%</li> <li>近 1 月：-31.14%</li> <li>近 3 月：-32.85%</li> <li>近 6 月：-49.82%</li> <li>今年以來：-33.09%</li></ul></section></main>",
